 />\n認同唔該用盡任何途徑spread開去<br />\n祝大家武運亨通<br />\n<br />\nBTW如果見人偷野建議先警告<br />\n唔聽就當係鬼獅鳥左佢"},{"pid":"029052850a5c6b83447f0a9192d54c6620a5752a","tid":1622994,"uid":238598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T22:43:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec584f5fbfdcd6269a72dbadf37614995e696ec","tid":1622994,"uid":54323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T22:58:23.000Z","msg":"笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba42100a646ff4b7b10014e8895e1b58686eb906","tid":1622994,"uid":36942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56a6837efcf2d46a5b8252eadbec4babb5dc2c4","tid":1622994,"uid":281388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:47:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567ae6d60c5bf4a56d3c049f6ad5c4c5c9c1915a","tid":1622994,"uid":222269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:17:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a473c0ec5056e6971285123c87ee695a0b2e14df","tid":1622994,"uid":58409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:59:12.000Z","msg":"大家今日點出去呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}